title: Rwanda Manufacturing Production
description: Manufacturing Production in Rwanda increased 14.20 percent in September of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Manufacturing Production in Rwanda averaged 9.97 percent from 2007 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 102.50 percent in April of 2021 and a record low of -43.50 percent in April of 2020. This page provides - Rwanda Manufacturing Production- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Institute of Statistics of Rwanda
